{"tid":801271,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]部腦開唔到","createTime":"2018-08-31T13:17:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T19:11:40.000Z","uid":46500,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5feef3c5938df24e4aff2c5dcbd3ba04c1f76654","tid":801271,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:17:08.000Z","msg":"小弟部坐枱機由琴日開始開得幾分鐘就突然斷電 一開始以為多塵 剩係拎個掃掃下 結果連開都開唔到 㩒完power 開左幾秒自動熄 過幾秒又自己開 再過幾秒又熄...<br />\n<br />\n之後將火牛d線逐條試 試完又開到用左幾個鐘 打hots都冇問題<br />\n<br />\n今日放工返來部機又係咁<br />\n<br />\n究竟死底版定死牛?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n隻牛1年前換 gx550來 一路都冇overload問題<br />\n<br />\n底版就由4年前有部機到宜家<br />\n<br />\n會唔會仲有其他原因?"},{"pid":"dd243f813860815baf88e1d8e7787d260e07361d","tid":801271,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:38:02.000Z","msg":"求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee76c736d9aa1ee2b96d88eefd734fc0e8e4c51f","tid":801271,"uid":90301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:52:32.000Z","msg":"係唔係㩒開機-&gt;風扇轉(冇畫面)-&gt;風扇停-&gt;自動再開機-&gt;風扇轉(冇畫面)-&gt;無限loop?<br />\n我之前成日都會咁，我拎條ram出黎換下槽插就解決咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c3149beb911ea748a1592f4541c8a53fe80ae24","tid":801271,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"ee76c736d9aa1ee2b96d88eefd734fc0e8e4c51f","tid":801271,"uid":90301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:52:32.000Z","msg":"係唔係㩒開機-&gt;風扇轉(冇畫面)-&gt;風扇停-&gt;自動再開機-&gt;風扇轉(冇畫面)-&gt;無限loop?<br />\n我之前成日都會咁，我拎條ram出黎換下槽插就解決咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T16:04:52.000Z","msg":"吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.